OL,6,FHuman remains found in a south London
OL,7,Fpark have been identified by police as
OL,8,Fa 38-year-old woman.
OL,10,FSarah Mayhew, from Croydon, last
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,13,FA 44-year old man and a 48-year-old
OL,14,Fwoman on suspicion of murder and
OL,15,Fremain in custody.
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Martin Thorpe, who
OL,18,Fis leading the investigation, said:
OL,19,F"My thoughts are with Sarah's family
OL,20,Fas they deal with this heartbreaking
OL,21,Fnews.
